<h1 class="has-text-align-center"><strong>7 Poderosos Programas de Fidelização de Clientes para E-commerce</strong></h1>
<div class="post-content-category"><a href="https://sleeknote.com/pt-pt/blog/category/growth-marketing" rel="category tag">Growth Marketing</a></div>


<figure class="wp-block-image alignwide size-large"><img width="1024" height="437" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Customer-Loyalty-Programs-Wordpress-1024x437.jpg" alt="Customer Loyalty Programs [Wordpress]" class="wp-image-90589" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Customer-Loyalty-Programs-Wordpress-1024x437.jpg 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Customer-Loyalty-Programs-Wordpress-300x128.jpg 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Customer-Loyalty-Programs-Wordpress-768x328.jpg 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Customer-Loyalty-Programs-Wordpress-1536x656.jpg 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Customer-Loyalty-Programs-Wordpress-380x162.jpg 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Customer-Loyalty-Programs-Wordpress-600x256.jpg 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Customer-Loyalty-Programs-Wordpress-760x325.jpg 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Customer-Loyalty-Programs-Wordpress-1440x615.jpg 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Customer-Loyalty-Programs-Wordpress-960x410.jpg 960w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Customer-Loyalty-Programs-Wordpress-82x35.jpg 82w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Customer-Loyalty-Programs-Wordpress-117x50.jpg 117w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Customer-Loyalty-Programs-Wordpress-740x316.jpg 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Customer-Loyalty-Programs-Wordpress-220x94.jpg 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Customer-Loyalty-Programs-Wordpress-385x164.jpg 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Customer-Loyalty-Programs-Wordpress.jpg 1920w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure>


<div id="preamble-block_5e96d6ebea423" class="block-preamble"><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Fidelizar clientes a uma marca nem sempre é fácil. Você precisa de uma estratégia escalável para incentivar os clientes a comprar de você de novo e de novo&#8230;</span></p>
</div>






<p>E é aí que entram os programas de fidelização do cliente.</p>



<p>Com a iniciativa correta, você pode fazer com que o cliente que comprou uma vez se torne um cliente fiel, e manter a sua marca em primeiro lugar.</p>



<p>Nesta postagem, vou mostrar a você como as principais empresas de e-commerce estão usando diferentes tipos de programas de fidelidade para fazer mais vendas, melhorar a retenção de clientes, e construir relacionamentos mais fortes com os clientes.</p>



<p>Vamos lá.</p>


<div id="contentupgrade-block_5e96d713ea424" class="block-content-upgrade">
    <div class="text">
        <p class="text-pretitle">RECURSOS GRATUITOS</p>
        <h2 class="text-title">Quer mais Estratégias de Marketing e Crescimento?</h2>
        <div class="text-content"><p>Acesse nossas ferramentas gratuitas de marketing de crescimento e aumente exponencialmente seu tráfego hoje mesmo (inclui recursos além dos que você pode encontrar na postagem do blog).</p>
</div>
                    <a onClick="SleekNote.triggerOnclick('00c91b9b-1dbc-48da-8d77-1dd2cfc8355b');" href="javascript:void(0);" class="text-link" title="Baixe as Ferramentas de Marketing e Crescimento →">Baixe as Ferramentas de Marketing e Crescimento →</a>
            </div>
    <div class="image">
        <img src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Grow-Your-Email-List@2x-1.png" title="Quer mais Estratégias de Marketing e Crescimento?">    </div>
</div>


<h2><strong>7 Exemplos de Programas de Fidelização de Clientes que Você Precisa Ver</strong></h2>



<p><a href="#1">Programa de Pontos (The North Face)</a></p>



<p><a href="#2">Programa Pago (Barnes &amp; Noble)</a></p>



<p><a href="#3">Programa de Caridade (The Body Shop)</a></p>



<p><a href="#4">Programa de Níveis (e.l.f.)</a></p>



<p><a href="#5">Programa de Parceria (Nike)</a></p>



<p><a href="#6">Programa de Comunidade (Sephora)</a></p>



<p><a href="#7">Programa de Assinatura (Bean Box)</a></p>



<h2 id="1"><strong>1. Programa de Pontos (The North Face)</strong></h2>



<p>O programa de pontos é baseado em um princípio simples: quanto mais você gasta, mais pontos você ganha em troca.&nbsp;</p>



<p>Sempre que um cliente faz uma compra em seu site (ou em sua loja física, se você tiver uma), eles ganham um determinado número de pontos dependendo do quanto tiverem gasto.&nbsp;</p>



<p><a href="https://www.thenorthface.com/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow">The North Face</a> usa esse tipo de sistema em seu programa de recompensas inteligentemente chamado de “VIPeak”:</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="744" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/The-North-Face-VIPeak-Program-1024x744.jpg" alt="The North Face VIPeak Program" class="wp-image-90625" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/The-North-Face-VIPeak-Program-1024x744.jpg 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/The-North-Face-VIPeak-Program-300x218.jpg 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/The-North-Face-VIPeak-Program-768x558.jpg 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/The-North-Face-VIPeak-Program-380x276.jpg 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/The-North-Face-VIPeak-Program-600x436.jpg 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/The-North-Face-VIPeak-Program-760x552.jpg 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/The-North-Face-VIPeak-Program-48x35.jpg 48w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/The-North-Face-VIPeak-Program-69x50.jpg 69w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/The-North-Face-VIPeak-Program-674x490.jpg 674w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/The-North-Face-VIPeak-Program-220x160.jpg 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/The-North-Face-VIPeak-Program-385x280.jpg 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/The-North-Face-VIPeak-Program.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>Eles fazem com que o cliente entenda facilmente como o programa de recompensas funciona:</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="243" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/The-North-Face-Loyalty-Program-1-1024x243.jpg" alt="The North Face Loyalty Program" class="wp-image-90621" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/The-North-Face-Loyalty-Program-1-1024x243.jpg 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/The-North-Face-Loyalty-Program-1-300x71.jpg 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/The-North-Face-Loyalty-Program-1-768x182.jpg 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/The-North-Face-Loyalty-Program-1-380x90.jpg 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/The-North-Face-Loyalty-Program-1-600x143.jpg 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/The-North-Face-Loyalty-Program-1-760x181.jpg 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/The-North-Face-Loyalty-Program-1-147x35.jpg 147w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/The-North-Face-Loyalty-Program-1-211x50.jpg 211w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/The-North-Face-Loyalty-Program-1-740x176.jpg 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/The-North-Face-Loyalty-Program-1-220x52.jpg 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/The-North-Face-Loyalty-Program-1-385x91.jpg 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/The-North-Face-Loyalty-Program-1.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>Os clientes ganham 10 pontos para cada $1 gasto nas lojas online ou de varejo., e cinco pontos para cada $1 gasto nos outlets. Depois, os clientes podem usar esses pontos em suas futuras compras.</p>



<p>Para aumentar ainda mais o envolvimento do cliente, a The North Face também desenvolveu um app onde os usuários podem gerenciar suas contas, comprar novos produtos, verificar os pontos e trocá-los por recompensas.</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="674" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/The-North-Face-App-1024x674.jpg" alt="The North Face App" class="wp-image-90617" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/The-North-Face-App-1024x674.jpg 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/The-North-Face-App-300x198.jpg 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/The-North-Face-App-768x506.jpg 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/The-North-Face-App-380x250.jpg 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/The-North-Face-App-600x395.jpg 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/The-North-Face-App-760x500.jpg 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/The-North-Face-App-53x35.jpg 53w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/The-North-Face-App-76x50.jpg 76w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/The-North-Face-App-740x487.jpg 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/The-North-Face-App-220x145.jpg 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/The-North-Face-App-385x253.jpg 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/The-North-Face-App.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>Ao recompensar os clientes com pontos que eles podem trocar por recompensas, você não só aumenta o valor médio de compra dos clientes; também os encoraja a investir em sua marca, o que reduz a probabilidade de trocarem você por um concorrente.</p>



<p>Lembre-se: mantenha seu sistema de pontos simples para que seja fácil para os clientes determinar o valor de seus pontos.</p>



<div class="wp-block-group is-style-shadow-box has-sleek-light-grey-background-color has-background"><div class="wp-block-group__inner-container">
<h3><strong>Importante</strong></h3>



<p>Se você quer implantar um sistema de pontos para a sua loja online, certifique-se de implementá-lo no meio on-line e off-line se você tiver lojas físicas. Você pode usar um software como o <a href="https://smile.io/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow">Smile.io</a> para estabelecer seu sistema de pontos (e outras recompensas).&nbsp;</p>



<p>O seu sistema de pontos deve ser simples, para que os clientes entendam como calculá-lo. Por exemplo, $1 pode ser um ponto. Dessa forma, os clientes podem ver o valor diretamente e não precisam calcular o número de pontos que cada compra dará a eles.</p>
</div></div>



<h2 id="2"><strong>2. Programa Pago (Barnes &amp; Noble)</strong></h2>



<p>Os programas pagos exigem que os clientes paguem uma taxa mensal ou anual para entrar no seu clube de membros VIP.&nbsp;</p>



<p>Para que esse tipo de programa de fidelidade seja eficaz, você precisa de uma base de clientes sólida.&nbsp;</p>



<p>É improvável que novos clientes paguem para entrar em programas de recompensas, portanto, use esse tipo de programa para manter os clientes atuais e que compram frequentemente.</p>



<p>O seu programa pago deve incluir benefícios que sejam exclusivos aos membros, do contrário irá perder seu valor.&nbsp;</p>



<p>Aqui está um exemplo da <a href="https://www.barnesandnoble.com/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow">Barnes &amp; Noble</a>:</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="642" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Barnes-and-Noble-Loyalty-Program-1024x642.jpg" alt="Barnes and Noble Loyalty Program" class="wp-image-90573" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Barnes-and-Noble-Loyalty-Program-1024x642.jpg 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Barnes-and-Noble-Loyalty-Program-300x188.jpg 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Barnes-and-Noble-Loyalty-Program-768x481.jpg 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Barnes-and-Noble-Loyalty-Program-380x238.jpg 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Barnes-and-Noble-Loyalty-Program-600x376.jpg 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Barnes-and-Noble-Loyalty-Program-760x476.jpg 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Barnes-and-Noble-Loyalty-Program-56x35.jpg 56w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Barnes-and-Noble-Loyalty-Program-80x50.jpg 80w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Barnes-and-Noble-Loyalty-Program-740x464.jpg 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Barnes-and-Noble-Loyalty-Program-220x138.jpg 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Barnes-and-Noble-Loyalty-Program-385x241.jpg 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Barnes-and-Noble-Loyalty-Program.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>Seu programa VIP custa $25 ao ano, e oferece <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/discount-strategy" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">descontos</a>, frete grátis e outros benefícios.</p>



<p>Mas como você consegue pessoas que paguem $25 para entrar em um programa de fidelidade?&nbsp;</p>



<p>Mostrando o valor do seu programa em comparação com o custo, como a Barnes &amp; Noble faz:</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="270" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Barnes-and-Noble-Bonus-1024x270.jpg" alt="Barnes and Noble Bonus" class="wp-image-90569" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Barnes-and-Noble-Bonus-1024x270.jpg 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Barnes-and-Noble-Bonus-300x79.jpg 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Barnes-and-Noble-Bonus-768x202.jpg 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Barnes-and-Noble-Bonus-380x100.jpg 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Barnes-and-Noble-Bonus-600x158.jpg 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Barnes-and-Noble-Bonus-760x200.jpg 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Barnes-and-Noble-Bonus-133x35.jpg 133w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Barnes-and-Noble-Bonus-190x50.jpg 190w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Barnes-and-Noble-Bonus-740x195.jpg 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Barnes-and-Noble-Bonus-220x58.jpg 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Barnes-and-Noble-Bonus-385x101.jpg 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Barnes-and-Noble-Bonus.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>Quando o valor do seu programa de fidelidade supera o custo, as pessoas irão entrar.</p>



<p>E para dar um empurrãozinho final, você pode usar os <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/customer-testimonials" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">depoimentos de clientes</a> dos membros atuais como <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/social-proof" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">prova social</a>:</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="956" height="1024" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Barnes-and-Noble-Testimonials-956x1024.jpg" alt="Barnes and Noble Testimonials" class="wp-image-90577" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Barnes-and-Noble-Testimonials-956x1024.jpg 956w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Barnes-and-Noble-Testimonials-280x300.jpg 280w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Barnes-and-Noble-Testimonials-768x823.jpg 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Barnes-and-Noble-Testimonials-380x407.jpg 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Barnes-and-Noble-Testimonials-600x643.jpg 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Barnes-and-Noble-Testimonials-760x814.jpg 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Barnes-and-Noble-Testimonials-33x35.jpg 33w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Barnes-and-Noble-Testimonials-47x50.jpg 47w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Barnes-and-Noble-Testimonials-457x490.jpg 457w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Barnes-and-Noble-Testimonials-220x236.jpg 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Barnes-and-Noble-Testimonials-385x413.jpg 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Barnes-and-Noble-Testimonials.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 956px) 100vw, 956px" /></figure></div>



<div class="wp-block-group is-style-shadow-box has-sleek-light-grey-background-color has-background"><div class="wp-block-group__inner-container">
<h3><strong>Importante</strong></h3>



<p>Quando oferecer um programa pago, mostre aos clientes que o valor do programa é maior do que o seu custo. Usar a prova social dos membros existentes para enfatizar o seu valor também ajuda..</p>
</div></div>



<h2 id="3"><strong>3. Programa de Caridade (The Body Shop)</strong></h2>



<p>Um programa de fidelidade não precisa incluir descontos.</p>



<p>Em vez disso, você pode incorporar os valores da sua empresa em seu programa para construir uma relação mais forte com seus clientes. Na verdade, se você estrutura um programa de fidelidade baseado em valores <em>mútuos</em>, é mais provável que os clientes queiram se tornar fiéis à marca.</p>



<p>A <a href="https://www.thebodyshop.com/en-us/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow">The Body Shop</a> adotou essa metodologia ao tornar o bem-estar animal parte do seu programa.</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="636" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/The-Body-Shop-Loyalty-Program-1024x636.jpg" alt="The Body Shop Loyalty Program" class="wp-image-90637" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/The-Body-Shop-Loyalty-Program-1024x636.jpg 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/The-Body-Shop-Loyalty-Program-300x186.jpg 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/The-Body-Shop-Loyalty-Program-768x477.jpg 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/The-Body-Shop-Loyalty-Program-380x236.jpg 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/The-Body-Shop-Loyalty-Program-600x373.jpg 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/The-Body-Shop-Loyalty-Program-760x472.jpg 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/The-Body-Shop-Loyalty-Program-56x35.jpg 56w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/The-Body-Shop-Loyalty-Program-81x50.jpg 81w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/The-Body-Shop-Loyalty-Program-740x459.jpg 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/The-Body-Shop-Loyalty-Program-220x137.jpg 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/The-Body-Shop-Loyalty-Program-385x239.jpg 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/The-Body-Shop-Loyalty-Program.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>Além de ganhar recompensas e benefícios VIP, os membros têm outro benefício exclusivo:</p>



<p><em>Eles podem escolher doar suas recompensas para a </em><a href="https://www.bornfreeusa.org/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow"><em>Born Free USA</em></a><em> (uma instituição de caridade para o bem-estar animal).</em></p>



<p>Essa não é uma decisão aleatória.&nbsp;</p>



<p>Um valor fundamental da <a href="http://www.thebodyshop.com/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow">The Body Shop</a> semelhantemente é a responsabilidade ambiental:</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="229" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/The-Body-Shop-Commitment-1024x229.jpg" alt="The Body Shop Commitment" class="wp-image-90613" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/The-Body-Shop-Commitment-1024x229.jpg 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/The-Body-Shop-Commitment-300x67.jpg 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/The-Body-Shop-Commitment-768x172.jpg 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/The-Body-Shop-Commitment-380x85.jpg 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/The-Body-Shop-Commitment-600x134.jpg 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/The-Body-Shop-Commitment-760x170.jpg 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/The-Body-Shop-Commitment-157x35.jpg 157w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/The-Body-Shop-Commitment-224x50.jpg 224w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/The-Body-Shop-Commitment-740x165.jpg 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/The-Body-Shop-Commitment-220x49.jpg 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/The-Body-Shop-Commitment-385x86.jpg 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/The-Body-Shop-Commitment.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>Os clientes da The Body Shop compartilham esses valores, o que torna a opção da doação ainda mais relevante para os clientes.</p>



<p>Esse tipo de programa cria uma oportunidade única para você se conectar com seus clientes em um nível mais profundo, fortalecendo seu relacionamento com eles.</p>



<div class="wp-block-group is-style-shadow-box has-sleek-light-grey-background-color has-background"><div class="wp-block-group__inner-container">
<h3><strong>Importante</strong></h3>



<p>Quando você oferece benefícios exclusivos aos membros, garanta que esses benefícios estejam de acordo com os valores da sua marca. Quando você cria valores em comum e usa os benefícios VIP para transmitir e fortalecer esses valores, seus clientes permanecerão fiéis ao seu negócio.</p>
</div></div>



<h2 id="4"><strong>4. Programa de Níveis (e.l.f.)</strong></h2>



<p>O sistema de níveis é baseado em níveis de fidelidade.&nbsp;</p>



<p>Falando de outra maneira, quanto mais fiéis seus clientes forem à sua marca (leia: quanto mais eles comprarem de você), maiores recompensas eles receberão.&nbsp;</p>



<p>Oferecer níveis em um programa de fidelização é uma ótima maneira de envolver os clientes e manter sua marca mais lembrada. Além disso, aborda as ideias da gamificação onde os membros alcançam níveis mais altos quanto mais eles “jogam”.</p>



<p>Pegue esse exemplo da <a href="https://www.elfcosmetics.com/beauty-squad/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow">e.l.f.</a>:</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="775" height="1024" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/ELF-Cosmetics-Loyalty-Program-775x1024.jpg" alt="ELF Cosmetics Loyalty Program" class="wp-image-90593" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/ELF-Cosmetics-Loyalty-Program-775x1024.jpg 775w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/ELF-Cosmetics-Loyalty-Program-227x300.jpg 227w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/ELF-Cosmetics-Loyalty-Program-768x1014.jpg 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/ELF-Cosmetics-Loyalty-Program-1163x1536.jpg 1163w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/ELF-Cosmetics-Loyalty-Program-380x502.jpg 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/ELF-Cosmetics-Loyalty-Program-600x793.jpg 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/ELF-Cosmetics-Loyalty-Program-760x1004.jpg 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/ELF-Cosmetics-Loyalty-Program-26x35.jpg 26w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/ELF-Cosmetics-Loyalty-Program-38x50.jpg 38w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/ELF-Cosmetics-Loyalty-Program-371x490.jpg 371w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/ELF-Cosmetics-Loyalty-Program-220x291.jpg 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/ELF-Cosmetics-Loyalty-Program-385x509.jpg 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/ELF-Cosmetics-Loyalty-Program.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px" /></figure></div>



<p>Seu clube de fidelidade Beauty Squad tem três níveis:&nbsp;</p>



<ol><li>Glow Getter;</li><li>Rising Star; e</li><li>A-Lister.</li></ol>



<p>Quanto mais pontos um membro tem, mais exclusivas são as recompensas que ele receberá. A exclusividade do nível mais alto é um grande incentivo para que os clientes comprem mais.</p>



<p>Se você quer motivar os membros a alcançar níveis mais altos, inclua os percentuais para cada um deles, indicando quantos membros chegaram em cada nível.</p>



<p>Isso serve como um estímulo para que os membros alcancem níveis mais altos para ganhar status social entre os membros que pertencem àquele grupo.</p>



<div class="wp-block-group is-style-shadow-box has-sleek-light-grey-background-color has-background"><div class="wp-block-group__inner-container">
<h3><strong>Importante</strong></h3>



<p>Crie um programa que permita aos membros crescer com base em sua fidelidade como cliente. Você pode basear o seu programa de níveis em pontos, na frequência em que as pessoas compram ou em outras métricas de engajamento importantes. Certifique-se de que a exclusividade e o valor dos benefícios aumentem a cada nível para encorajar os membros a subir de nível.</p>
</div></div>



<h2 id="5"><strong>5. Programa de Parceria (Nike)</strong></h2>



<p>Com o aumento da popularidade dos programas de fidelidade, os clientes estão buscando maior flexibilidade nas recompensas.&nbsp;</p>



<p>Ao fazer parcerias com outras empresas, você pode criar um programa de fidelidade que não apenas ofereça mais oportunidades aos clientes, mas que também facilite a criação de novos relacionamentos de negócios.&nbsp;</p>



<p><a href="https://www.loyalty.com/home/insights/colloquy-speaks" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow">Uma pesquisa</a> descobriu que 68% dos millennials permanecem fiéis a um programa que oferece a eles as maiores recompensas.&nbsp;</p>



<p>Estabelecer parcerias com outras empresas dá a você essa possibilidade.</p>



<p>Se olharmos o programa de fidelidade da <a href="https://www.nike.com/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow">Nike</a>, você vai ver que eles oferecem aos membros benefícios exclusivos que incluem parcerias com <a href="https://www.apple.com/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow">Apple</a>, <a href="https://classpass.com/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow">Classpass</a>, e <a href="https://www.headspace.com/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow">Headspace</a>.</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="594" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Nike-Earn-Benefits-1024x594.png" alt="Nike Earn Benefits" class="wp-image-90597" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Nike-Earn-Benefits-1024x594.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Nike-Earn-Benefits-300x174.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Nike-Earn-Benefits-768x445.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Nike-Earn-Benefits-380x220.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Nike-Earn-Benefits-600x348.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Nike-Earn-Benefits-760x441.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Nike-Earn-Benefits-60x35.png 60w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Nike-Earn-Benefits-86x50.png 86w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Nike-Earn-Benefits-740x429.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Nike-Earn-Benefits-220x128.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Nike-Earn-Benefits-385x223.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Nike-Earn-Benefits.png 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>Esses apps não foram escolhidos ao acaso; todos eles são relevantes à missão da Nike, que é inspirar atletas do mundo todo.</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="433" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Nike-Mission-Statement-1024x433.jpg" alt="Nike Mission Statement" class="wp-image-90633" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Nike-Mission-Statement-1024x433.jpg 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Nike-Mission-Statement-300x127.jpg 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Nike-Mission-Statement-768x324.jpg 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Nike-Mission-Statement-380x161.jpg 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Nike-Mission-Statement-600x254.jpg 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Nike-Mission-Statement-760x321.jpg 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Nike-Mission-Statement-83x35.jpg 83w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Nike-Mission-Statement-118x50.jpg 118w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Nike-Mission-Statement-740x313.jpg 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Nike-Mission-Statement-220x93.jpg 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Nike-Mission-Statement-385x163.jpg 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Nike-Mission-Statement.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>A Nike também tem diversos apps de treinamento diferentes para ajudar os membros a alcançar seus objetivos.</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="445" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Nike-Workout-Rewards-1024x445.jpg" alt="Nike Workout Rewards" class="wp-image-90601" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Nike-Workout-Rewards-1024x445.jpg 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Nike-Workout-Rewards-300x130.jpg 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Nike-Workout-Rewards-768x333.jpg 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Nike-Workout-Rewards-380x165.jpg 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Nike-Workout-Rewards-600x261.jpg 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Nike-Workout-Rewards-760x330.jpg 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Nike-Workout-Rewards-81x35.jpg 81w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Nike-Workout-Rewards-115x50.jpg 115w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Nike-Workout-Rewards-740x321.jpg 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Nike-Workout-Rewards-220x96.jpg 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Nike-Workout-Rewards-385x167.jpg 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Nike-Workout-Rewards.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>A Nike sabe que quanto mais sucesso seus clientes tiverem em seus treinamentos mais fiéis eles serão.&nbsp;</p>



<p>Por quê?</p>



<p><em>Porque as pessoas sempre vinculam seu sucesso a alguém ou algo que fez a diferença.</em></p>



<p>Por exemplo, se você quer aprender a falar um novo idioma e para isso você usa um software como <a href="https://www.duolingo.com/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow">Duolingo</a>, você vai atribuir o seu sucesso (ou fracasso) ao Duolingo.</p>



<p>O mesmo vale para a Nike. Eles ajudam seus consumidores a obter melhores resultados nos treinos, e seus consumidores atribuem seus resultados à Nike e seus parceiros.</p>



<div class="wp-block-group is-style-shadow-box has-sleek-light-grey-background-color has-background"><div class="wp-block-group__inner-container">
<h3><strong>Importante</strong></h3>



<p>Faça parceria com outras empresas que ofereçam flexibilidade de benefícios para ajudar seus membros a atingir seus objetivos ou vencer seus desafios. É importante que você coloque seu produto como um “ingrediente” principal para alcançar esses objetivos. Quando o seu produto ajuda seus membros em seus objetivos e desafios, eles comprarão mais de você.</p>
</div></div>



<h2 id="6"><strong>6. Programa de Comunidade (Sephora)</strong></h2>



<p>Quando falamos sobre programas de fidelização de clientes, não podemos deixar de falar da <a href="https://www.sephora.com/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow">Sephora</a>.</p>



<p>A Sephora tem um programa de fidelidade abrangente (Beauty Insider) que oferece muitos benefícios diferentes:</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="996" height="1024" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Sephora-Rewards-996x1024.jpg" alt="Sephora Rewards" class="wp-image-90609" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Sephora-Rewards-996x1024.jpg 996w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Sephora-Rewards-292x300.jpg 292w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Sephora-Rewards-768x790.jpg 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Sephora-Rewards-380x391.jpg 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Sephora-Rewards-600x617.jpg 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Sephora-Rewards-760x782.jpg 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Sephora-Rewards-34x35.jpg 34w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Sephora-Rewards-49x50.jpg 49w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Sephora-Rewards-476x490.jpg 476w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Sephora-Rewards-220x226.jpg 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Sephora-Rewards-385x396.jpg 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Sephora-Rewards.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 996px) 100vw, 996px" /></figure></div>



<p>Além de usar um programa de níveis e um sistema de pontos, o programa de fidelidade da Sephora também dá aos membros o acesso exclusivo à comunidade de pessoas com a mesma opinião.</p>



<p>Nessa comunidade, os membros podem se conectar uns com os outros, encontrar inspiração, cadastrar-se em eventos exclusivos e muito mais.</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="800" height="733" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Sephora-Community-Benefits-1.jpg" alt="Sephora Community Benefits" class="wp-image-90605" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Sephora-Community-Benefits-1.jpg 800w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Sephora-Community-Benefits-1-300x275.jpg 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Sephora-Community-Benefits-1-768x704.jpg 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Sephora-Community-Benefits-1-380x348.jpg 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Sephora-Community-Benefits-1-600x550.jpg 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Sephora-Community-Benefits-1-760x696.jpg 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Sephora-Community-Benefits-1-38x35.jpg 38w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Sephora-Community-Benefits-1-55x50.jpg 55w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Sephora-Community-Benefits-1-535x490.jpg 535w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Sephora-Community-Benefits-1-220x202.jpg 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Sephora-Community-Benefits-1-385x353.jpg 385w" sizes="(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px" /></figure></div>



<p>A Sephora utiliza o seu clube de fidelidade para construir uma comunidade para a marca onde os usuários podem interagir uns com os outros e com a Sephora.&nbsp;</p>



<p>Ao criar uma plataforma como essa, a Sephora tem acesso à visão de muitos consumidores e pode usá-la para o desenvolvimento de produtos e a otimização de outros aspectos.&nbsp;</p>



<div class="wp-block-group is-style-shadow-box has-sleek-light-grey-background-color has-background"><div class="wp-block-group__inner-container">
<h3><strong>Importante</strong></h3>



<p>Crie uma plataforma na qual os membros possam interagir uns com os outros, compartilhar ideias, inspirar-se, receber feedback e muito mais. Esse tipo de programa funciona com qualquer marca, desde que você encoraje as conversas relevantes para sua marca e produtos.</p>
</div></div>



<h2 id="7"><strong>7. Programa de Assinatura (Bean Box)</strong></h2>



<p>Existe um novo tipo de programa de fidelização…</p>



<p>&#8230;é o programa de assinatura.</p>



<p>Este não é o tipo de programa de fidelidade tradicional onde você oferece recompensas e benefícios.</p>



<p>Em vez disso, você oferece seus produtos mediante uma assinatura.</p>



<p>Vamos pegar a <a href="https://beanbox.co/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow">Bean Box</a> como exemplo:</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="672" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Bean-Box-Subscription-1024x672.jpg" alt="Bean Box Subscription" class="wp-image-90581" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Bean-Box-Subscription-1024x672.jpg 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Bean-Box-Subscription-300x197.jpg 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Bean-Box-Subscription-768x504.jpg 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Bean-Box-Subscription-380x250.jpg 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Bean-Box-Subscription-600x394.jpg 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Bean-Box-Subscription-760x499.jpg 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Bean-Box-Subscription-53x35.jpg 53w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Bean-Box-Subscription-76x50.jpg 76w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Bean-Box-Subscription-740x486.jpg 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Bean-Box-Subscription-220x144.jpg 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Bean-Box-Subscription-385x253.jpg 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Bean-Box-Subscription.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>Para aumentar a fidelidade do cliente, a Bean Box oferece diferentes tipos de grãos de café como assinatura e os clientes não precisam se preocupar em ficar sem café. (Eu já vi o que acontece quando a máquina de café no escritório da Sleeknote quebra. NÃO é algo legal de se ver.)</p>



<p>Ao vender café por assinatura, a Bean Box aumenta a longevidade de seus clientes. Por hora, eles usam um incentivo de “Economize 20%” para que os clientes escolham o plano de 6 meses em vez do plano de um mês.</p>



<p>Enfim, convidar os clientes para firmar um compromisso por 6 meses é mais vantajoso para a Bean Box do que se os clientes comprarem apenas uma vez.</p>



<div class="wp-block-group is-style-shadow-box has-sleek-light-grey-background-color has-background"><div class="wp-block-group__inner-container">
<h3><strong>Importante</strong></h3>



<p>Se o seu produto for adequado, você deveria tentar oferecer uma assinatura. Os consumidores estão buscando por conveniência acima de tudo. E quanto mais rápido e fácil eles tiverem aquilo que precisam em suas mãos, melhor. Você pode incentivar os clientes em potencial a optar por uma assinatura em vez de comprar apenas uma vez oferecendo a eles um desconto na assinatura.</p>
</div></div>



<div style="height:40px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>






